'''Snapchat'''是一款由[[斯坦福大学|斯坦福大学]]学生开发的{{link-en|图片分享|Photo sharing}}[[应用程序|软件应用]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Snapchat Team|url=http://www.snapchat.com/#|accessdate=7 February 2013|archive-date=2012-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121114040211/http://www.snapchat.com/|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Prigg|first=Mark|title=The :|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sciencetech/article-2256082/The-sexting-wars-The-Stanford-students-beating-Facebook-battle-self-destructing-pictures.html#axzz2KBWi2pxg|accessdate=7 February 2013|newspaper=Mail Online|date=2 January 2013|archive-date=2013-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131115051353/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sciencetech/article-2256082/The-sexting-wars-The-Stanford-students-beating-Facebook-battle-self-destructing-pictures.html#axzz2KBWi2pxg|dead-url=no}}</ref>。利用该应用程序，用户可以拍照、录制影片、撰寫文字和圖畫，并傳送到自己在该应用上的好友列表。这些照片及影片被称为“快照”（"Snaps"）。 用户在向好友发送“快照”时，可以设定一个限制好友访问“快照”的时间（截止2017年7月，用户可选择的时限是1秒至10秒之间，或無限<ref>{{cite web|title=Snapchat Hands-on: Send Photos Set to Self-Destruct|url=http://blog.laptopmag.com/hands-on-with-snapchat-send-photos-set-to-self-destruct|work=Laptop|publisher=TechMedia Network|accessdate=15 September 2013|author=Davey Alba|date=16 May 2012|archive-date=2013-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921054529/http://blog.laptopmag.com/hands-on-with-snapchat-send-photos-set-to-self-destruct|dead-url=yes}}</ref>），在这之后，这些“快照”会彻底从好友的设备上和snapchat上的服务器删除。

==用户群体==
Snapchat的主要用户群体是在13到25岁之间的青少年。自2012年10月起,40岁以上的用户群体亦开始持续增长。该应用经常会被用来向朋友发送自拍照，其中大約会有30%的照片被傳送至snapchat中的群组当中。<ref name="All Things, text overlay">{{cite news|title=Fast-Growing Photo-Messaging App Snapchat Launches on Android|url=http://allthingsd.com/20121029/fast-growing-photo-messaging-app-snapchat-launches-on-android/|accessdate=22 December 2012|newspaper=All Things D|date=29 October 2012|author=Liz Gannes|archive-date=2013-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130101043837/http://allthingsd.com/20121029/fast-growing-photo-messaging-app-snapchat-launches-on-android/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 公司的首席执行官斯皮格尔在2013年4月份的Dive into Mobile大会上表示，公司在美国擁有約80%的用戶<ref>{{cite news|title=Snapchat social app gains ground on Twitter with US iPhone owners|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/technology/appsblog/2013/jul/17/snapchat-app-growth-iphone-us|accessdate=21 July 2013|newspaper=The Guardian|date=17 July 2013|author=Stuart Dredge|archive-date=2013-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130722130042/http://www.guardian.co.uk/technology/appsblog/2013/jul/17/snapchat-app-growth-iphone-us|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==发展历史==
Snapchat是[[伊萬·斯皮格|伊萬·斯皮格]]和鲍比·墨菲在[[斯坦福大学|斯坦福大学]]产品设计中的一个班级作业而诞生的项目。2011年4月，伊萬·斯皮格在斯坦福大学的产品设计课上介绍了其最终方案的创意。<ref name="Forbes, touch">{{cite news|title=Snapchat: The Biggest No-Revenue Mobile App Since Instagram|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/jjcolao/2012/11/27/snapchat-the-biggest-no-revenue-mobile-app-since-instagram/|accessdate=25 December 2012|newspaper=Forbes|date=27 November 2012|author=J.J. Colao|archive-date=2018-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612164852/https://www.forbes.com/sites/jjcolao/2012/11/27/snapchat-the-biggest-no-revenue-mobile-app-since-instagram/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 并于2011年9月在斯皮格的父亲卧室中正式上线。<ref name="Forbes, touch" /><ref name="Review, trend">{{cite news|title=Snapchat a growing trend|url=http://www.udreview.com/snapchat-a-growing-trend-1.2939743#.UNYyv_xfN5Q|accessdate=22 December 2012|newspaper=University of Delaware Review|date=29 October 2012|author=Alexandria Murphy|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121102065408/http://www.udreview.com/snapchat-a-growing-trend-1.2939743#.UNYyv_xfN5Q|archivedate=2012年11月2日}}</ref>

在早期，Snapchat创业团队更专注于这款应用的易用性和技术挑战，而不是品牌和设计性<ref name="Forbes, touch" />。Snapchat的吉祥物被称作 "Ghostface Chillah", 这个名字来源于前[[武当帮|武当帮]]乐队成员的艺名“鬼脸杀手”（Ghostface Killah）。<ref name="Forbes, touch" />

2012年5月，每秒有25张快照从Snapchat上被发出<ref name="TC, billion snaps">{{cite news|title=You Know What's Cool? A Billion Snapchats: App Sees Over 20 Million Photos Shared Per Day, Releases On Android|url=http://techcrunch.com/2012/10/29/billion-snapchats/|accessdate=22 December 2012|newspaper=TechCrunch|date=29 October 2012|author=Billy Gallagher|archive-date=2014-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140108013327/http://techcrunch.com/2012/10/29/billion-snapchats/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2012年的11月28日，Snapchat的iOS客户端每天有超过2000万张快照被发送，总数已经超过10亿张。<ref name="TC, billion snaps" /><ref name="Upstart, 28 October">{{cite news|title=The app with self-destructing messages launches on Android|url=http://upstart.bizjournals.com/news/technology/2012/10/29/snapchat-launches-on-android.html|accessdate=22 December 2012|newspaper=Upstart Business Journal|date=29 October 2012|author=Michael del Castillo|archive-date=2013-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131007083611/http://upstart.bizjournals.com/news/technology/2012/10/29/snapchat-launches-on-android.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

在发展的初期Snapchat从{{tsl|en|Lightspeed Venture Partners|光速创投}}（Lightspeed Ventures）中拿到了48.5万美金的种子基金。<ref name="TC, billion snaps" /> 

截止2013年6月, Snapchat已经获得了超过6000万美元的[[风险投资|风险投资]]。<ref>{{cite web|title=Snapchat Snaps Up A $80M Series B Led By IVP At An $800M Valuation|url=http://techcrunch.com/2013/06/22/source-snapchat-snaps-up-80m-from-ivp-at-a-800m-valuation/|accessdate=2013-11-18|archive-date=2013-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131117174531/http://techcrunch.com/2013/06/22/source-snapchat-snaps-up-80m-from-ivp-at-a-800m-valuation/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2014年5月8日，Snapchat与美国[[联邦贸易委员会|联邦贸易委员会]]（FTC）就欺诈指控达成和解，该公司被控欺骗消费者，声称通过其应用发送的照片在一段时间后可永久消失，而实际上接收者可以用几种方法保存这些照片。该公司面临20年隐私监控。<ref>{{cite web|title=Snapchat就欺诈指控达成和解 面临20年隐私监控|url=http://finance.sina.com.cn/world/20140509/022819048325.shtml|publisher=新浪财经|accessdate=2014-05-09|archive-date=2014-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141014032105/http://finance.sina.com.cn/world/20140509/022819048325.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

